                    i have played endless hours of D2 LOD, and D2R (and D1 and D2 vanilla). I've seen runes up to Vex drop. Never an Ohm, Jah, Ber, Zod, Cham, etc. I'd estimate 3000 hours played where a high rune can drop. Thats probably less than the proffessional streamers, but still... Never had a windforce drop either.<br />
